&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Bank Senior Pharmacy Technicians &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Band 5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Solent NHS Trust are looking for motivated and enthusiastic pharmacy technicians to join their bank staff. This is an exciting opportunity for pharmacy technicians who have an interest in mental health and community services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post will be mainly based within the new dispensary at St Marys Community Health Campus in Portsmouth but may also involve working off-site providing services to wards and clinics. The ward based clinicalpharmacy team focuses on ensuring support for the patient and optimising their care with regards to medicines. You will work closely with multidisciplinary teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;For further details contact Shelagh Card, Dispensary Manager on 0300 123 6650.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
